These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, fanta, sprite, soy-milk
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, aconite, dahlia, sunflower
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, weightlifting, biathlon, sailing
4 different pets are kept: mouse, fish, rabbit, rat
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who growssunflower##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking soy-milk##2
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the owner of the mouse##1
4. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
5. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
6. the owner of the rabbit is the person drinking sprite##1
7. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
8. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
9. the person drinking fanta is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | fanta | soy-milk   | lemonade  | sprite  |
| Flower   | aconite    | sunflower    | poppy      | dahlia    |
| Sport   | sailing | weightlifting | biathlon | golf |
| Pet     | rat  | mouse       | fish    | rabbit     |

