The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, february, october, july
House: cottage, farmhouse, cape-cod, townhouse
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, russian, japanese, french
1. the french is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
3. the townhouse house is the russian##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the person who's birthday is in july is between the cape-cod house and the polish##2
6. the french is between the person who's birthday is in july and the townhouse house##2
7. the cottage house is on the far right##1
8. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
9. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage         | juice | soy-milk    | coffee  | mirinda    |
| Birthday   | august      | february  | july  | october |
| House           | townhouse      | cape-cod       | farmhouse      | cottage       |
| Nationality         | russian    | french | japanese | polish |

