6. the polish is the person who's birthday is in october##1
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
8. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who's birthday is in october##2
9. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the polish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
