 7. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 8. the person playing go is the person who likes white##1
 9. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person who growsballoon-flower and the person who likes lilac##2
10. the person who likes emerald is the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
