5. the owner of the dog is the owner of the dog##1
6. the owner of the frog is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
7. the owner of the frog is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
8. the person who likes blood-red is on the far right##1
9. the person who likes yellow is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
