 8. the fan country is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person who's sport is water-polo##2
 9. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the fan funk##1
10. the person driving the tram is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person who's sport is water-polo##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
